    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1358120/extras/c8e7924c6f12389fd6f98a523c731686.poster.avif?t=1749145146\" width=620 height=230 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1358120/extras/c8e7924c6f12389fd6f98a523c731686.webm?t=1749145146\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1358120/extras/c8e7924c6f12389fd6f98a523c731686.mp4?t=1749145146\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>《沙上之爪：狮魂之罪》是一款基于派对的RPG平台游戏，采用手绘2D图形。游戏背景设定在一个古老的世界中，灵感来自苏美尔-阿卡德、埃及和古代斯拉夫神话。这个世界充满了竞争激烈的城邦、古老的异教神灵、阴森的地下城和奇特的怪兽。游戏中没有人类；取而代之的是，角色被描绘成不同类型的拟人动物。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1358120/extras/ea9f61260cb67fb6f2bacebc25a835c1.poster.avif?t=1749145146\" width=173 height=209 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1358120/extras/ea9f61260cb67fb6f2bacebc25a835c1.webm?t=1749145146\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br><strong> 为狮魂之女 —— 乌鲁克的守护者 </strong><br><br>游戏的主要狮魂角色是居住在被征服的古代城邦乌鲁克的居民，她必须解救她的同族免于奴役之苦。她还需要从冥界女神埃列什基伽的无情掌控中拯救她的爱人，埃列什基伽与她的姐姐、生育女神伊希塔尔永远决裂。在此过程中，狮魂之女将参观邻近的城邦、探索相邻的领土，并承担（或不承担）许多小任务。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1358120/extras/b90e5fb874b4bb02803265383c8110ca.poster.avif?t=1749145146\" width=620 height=230 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1358120/extras/b90e5fb874b4bb02803265383c8110ca.webm?t=1749145146\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1358120/extras/b90e5fb874b4bb02803265383c8110ca.mp4?t=1749145146\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>《沙上之爪：狮魂之罪》通过为四名角色设计独特的战斗系统，增强了2D斩击游戏的机制。游戏无缝融合了2D平台游戏的玩法和基于派对的RPG的复杂元素，包括物品附魔、技能/职业强化以及角色在派对中的分工。当然，还有黑暗魔法的加入！<br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>一套独特的四名角色派对战斗系统，同时作为整体管理。<br></li><li>RPG元素丰富，包括装备的自定义，为团队成员选择适合的职业和16种可玩物种。<br></li><li>广阔且相互连接的游戏世界，拥有人口稠密的城邦、阴暗的地牢和宽敞的关卡。游戏过程中获得的新能力允许您到达先前无法进入的角落！<br></li><li>游戏的情节和支线任务将不会让任何人漠不关心。<br></li><li>嵌入式的收集卡牌游戏（CCG），融入主游戏，将补充主要玩法，让您在战斗和探索之间得以放松！</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1358120/extras/6957d48c448d22d19fdc72a615acf73c.poster.avif?t=1749145146\" width=620 height=190 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1358120/extras/6957d48c448d22d19fdc72a615acf73c.webm?t=1749145146\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1358120/extras/6957d48c448d22d19fdc72a615acf73c.mp4?t=1749145146\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1358120/extras/4d5876bfb93ecb31738bfce0368e8d3a.avif?t=1749145146\" width=620 height=200 /></span>",
